s\nshow a clear effect of real acceleration displayed in the adaptive Newton's\nmethod with cubic regularization on a set of regularized logistic regression\ninstances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Nov 2018 01:19:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 08:41:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2020 11:16:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-06"}
